Date: Mon, 1 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] NeoForge CreliaServer Entry Point

Integrates the Crelia server entry point with MinecraftServer. This patch
injects NeoForge lifecycle hooks (ServerLifecycleHooks) and Crelia region-
aware event dispatch into the Folia server bootstrap and tick loop.

Key changes:
- ServerLifecycleHooks.handleServerAboutToStart() called before Folia region init
- ServerLifecycleHooks.handleServerStarting() called before "Done" message
- ServerLifecycleHooks.handleServerStarted() called after "Done" message
- ServerLifecycleHooks.handleServerStopping() called during shutdown
- ServerLifecycleHooks.handleServerStopped() called in stopPart2
- NeoForge EventHooks.fireServerTickPre/Post for server tick events

diff --git a/src/main/java/net/minecraft/server/MinecraftServer.java b/src/main/java/net/minecraft/server/MinecraftServer.java
index 4ed79a51c89d54a7b2ab65a99b5b09cc807f4d4e..4b35c256ea3e6cf5405b950886ef621b4185dffb 100644
--- a/src/main/java/net/minecraft/server/MinecraftServer.java
+++ b/src/main/java/net/minecraft/server/MinecraftServer.java
